description: AMUNDI INDEX J.P. MORGAN GBI GLOBAL GOVIES - UCITS ETF DR seeks to replicate as closely as possible the performance of the J.P. Morgan Government Bond Index Global (GBI Global) Index, total return (coupons reinvested), in EUR, whether the trend is rising or falling. This ETF enables investors to benefit from an exposure to the fixed-rate government securities of 13 developed markets. For further information, please also refer to the KID and the fund prospectus.
name: Amundi Index J.P. Morgan GBI Global Govies UCITS ETF DR (C)
